data.value:
The Stock Portfolio sample creates a stock report for the stocks selected by the user at runtime. Data for the stocks are retrived from a database and populated in the Excel spreadsheets which are created using Essential XlsIO. The generated Excel sheet contains Hyperlinks, Comments, intuitive charts and images inserted.
Clicking the button below will result in a new Excel spreadsheet being generated using Essential XlsIO. At the end of the spreadsheet generation, an option will be provided to view the generated Excel file. Please note that you need to have an Excel viewer installed in order to view the generated Excel file.
